{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I want you now to imagine"},{"time":3000,"text":"a wearable robot"},{"time":6000,"text":"that gives you superhuman abilities,"},{"time":10000,"text":"or another one that takes wheelchair users"},{"time":14000,"text":"up standing and walking again."},{"time":18000,"text":"We at Berkeley Bionics"},{"time":21000,"text":"call these robots exoskeletons."},{"time":25000,"text":"These are nothing else"},{"time":27000,"text":"than something that you put on in the morning,"},{"time":30000,"text":"and it will give you extra strength,"},{"time":33000,"text":"and it will further enhance your speed,"},{"time":37000,"text":"and it will help you, for instance, to manage your balance."},{"time":41000,"text":"It is actually the true integration"},{"time":45000,"text":"of the man and the machine."},{"time":47000,"text":"But not only that --"},{"time":49000,"text":"it will integrate and network you"},{"time":51000,"text":"to the universe"},{"time":53000,"text":"and other devices out there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"This is just not some blue sky thinking."},{"time":58000,"text":"To show you now what we are working on"},{"time":61000,"text":"by starting out talking about"},{"time":63000,"text":"the American soldier,"},{"time":65000,"text":"that on average does carry about 100 lbs. on their backs,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and they are being asked to carry more equipment."},{"time":72000,"text":"Obviously, this is resulting"},{"time":75000,"text":"in some major complications --"},{"time":77000,"text":"back injuries, 30 percent of them --"},{"time":81000,"text":"chronic back injuries."},{"time":83000,"text":"So we thought we would look at this challenge"},{"time":86000,"text":"and create an exoskeleton"},{"time":89000,"text":"that would help deal with this issue."},{"time":93000,"text":"So let me now introduce to you HULC --"},{"time":97000,"text":"or the Human Universal"},{"time":99000,"text":"Load Carrier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"Soldier: With the HULC exoskeleton,"},{"time":104000,"text":"I can carry 200 lbs. over varied terrain"},{"time":106000,"text":"for many hours."},{"time":108000,"text":"Its flexible design allows for deep squats,"},{"time":110000,"text":"crawls and high-agility movements."},{"time":113000,"text":"It senses what I want to do, where I want to go,"},{"time":116000,"text":"and then augments my strength and endurance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"Eythor Bender: We are ready with our industry partner"},{"time":125000,"text":"to introduce this device,"},{"time":127000,"text":"this new exoskeleton this year."},{"time":130000,"text":"So this is for real."},{"time":132000,"text":"Now let's turn our heads"},{"time":135000,"text":"towards the wheelchair users,"},{"time":138000,"text":"something that I'm particularly passionate about."},{"time":141000,"text":"There are 68 million people"},{"time":143000,"text":"estimated to be in wheelchairs worldwide."},{"time":146000,"text":"This is about one percent of the total population."},{"time":149000,"text":"And that's actually a conservative estimate."},{"time":152000,"text":"We are talking here about, oftentimes,"},{"time":154000,"text":"very young individuals with spinal cord injuries,"},{"time":157000,"text":"that in the prime of their life -- 20s, 30s, 40s --"},{"time":160000,"text":"hit a wall"},{"time":162000,"text":"and the wheelchair's the only option."},{"time":164000,"text":"But it is also the aging population"},{"time":166000,"text":"that is multiplying in numbers."},{"time":169000,"text":"And the only option, pretty much --"},{"time":172000,"text":"when it's stroke or other complications --"},{"time":174000,"text":"is the wheelchair."},{"time":176000,"text":"And that is actually for the last 500 years,"},{"time":180000,"text":"since its very successful introduction, I must say."},{"time":184000,"text":"So we thought we would start"},{"time":186000,"text":"writing a brand new chapter"},{"time":189000,"text":"of mobility."},{"time":192000,"text":"Let me now introduce you to eLEGS"},{"time":195000,"text":"that is worn by Amanda Boxtel"},{"time":199000,"text":"that 19 years ago was spinal cord injured,"},{"time":203000,"text":"and as a result of that"},{"time":205000,"text":"she has not been able to walk"},{"time":207000,"text":"for 19 years until now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":213000,"text":"Amanda Boxtel: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"EB: Amanda is wearing our eLEGS set."},{"time":224000,"text":"It has sensors."},{"time":227000,"text":"It's completely non-invasive,"},{"time":229000,"text":"sensors in the crutches"},{"time":231000,"text":"that send signals back to our onboard computer"},{"time":234000,"text":"that is sitting here at her back."},{"time":237000,"text":"There are battery packs here as well"},{"time":239000,"text":"that power motors that are sitting at her hips,"},{"time":242000,"text":"as well as her knee joints,"},{"time":244000,"text":"that move her forward"},{"time":246000,"text":"in this kind of smooth and very natural gait."}]},{"cues":[{"time":253000,"text":"AB: I was 24 years old"},{"time":255000,"text":"and at the top of my game"},{"time":257000,"text":"when a freak summersault while downhill skiing"},{"time":260000,"text":"paralyzed me."},{"time":262000,"text":"In a split second,"},{"time":264000,"text":"I lost all sensation and movement"},{"time":267000,"text":"below my pelvis."},{"time":270000,"text":"Not long afterwards,"},{"time":272000,"text":"a doctor strode into my hospital room,"},{"time":275000,"text":"and he said, \"Amanda,"},{"time":277000,"text":"you'll never walk again.\""},{"time":281000,"text":"And that was 19 yeas ago."},{"time":284000,"text":"He robbed"},{"time":286000,"text":"every ounce of hope"},{"time":288000,"text":"from my being."},{"time":290000,"text":"Adaptive technology"},{"time":292000,"text":"has since enabled me"},{"time":294000,"text":"to learn how to downhill ski again,"},{"time":296000,"text":"to rock climb and even handcycle."},{"time":299000,"text":"But nothing has been invented"},{"time":303000,"text":"that enables me to walk,"},{"time":305000,"text":"until now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":320000,"text":"EB: As you can see,"},{"time":322000,"text":"we have the technology,"},{"time":324000,"text":"we have the platforms"},{"time":326000,"text":"to sit down and have discussions with you."},{"time":329000,"text":"It's in our hands,"},{"time":331000,"text":"and we have all the potential here"},{"time":335000,"text":"to change the lives"},{"time":337000,"text":"of future generations --"},{"time":339000,"text":"not only for the soldiers,"},{"time":343000,"text":"or for Amanda here and all the wheelchair users,"},{"time":347000,"text":"but for everyone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349000,"text":"AB: Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}